      "writtenOn": "2015-03-04T18:38:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Interesting. What is the rationale for the name change? I.e. GLDispatch.h is not too bad and consistent with the other names (i.e. GLEScmDispatch.h and GLESv2Dispatch.h)\n\nIn all cases, this should go into its own individual patch.",
